The paper discusses the training of neural networks, which is a topic that falls under several sub-categories of computer science. However, given the focus on overparameterization and convergence guarantees, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
